
## HEADERS

## PROJECT RULES

*   Project name: Хроніки Помийки (Chronicles of the Dumpster) - A Ukrainian Telegram Card Game Bot.
*   Target Locale: Ukrainian ("uk")

## TECH STACK

*   Python: 3.13 (Note: Originally specified as 3.14, but using 3.13 as 3.14 is not yet released. Update when 3.14 is stable.)
*   aiogram: 3.x
*   SQLAlchemy: Async
*   PostgreSQL: 17-alpine
*   Redis: alpine
*   Docker Compose
*   pydantic-settings
*   asyncpg
*   alembic
*   apscheduler
*   google-genai

## PROJECT DOCUMENTATION & CONTEXT SYSTEM

*   `.env.example`: Contains example environment variables.

## CODING STANDARDS

*   Use `pydantic-settings` for configuration management.
*   Output logs in JSON format using `structlog`.

## WORKFLOW & RELEASE RULES

## DEBUGGING

## INFRASTRUCTURE

*   Docker Compose should define `bot`, `db` (PostgreSQL), and `redis` services.
*   Docker container must wait for Postgres and Redis to be healthy before starting the bot.
*   Use named volumes for `pg_data` and `redis_data` to persist data.